{"tid":1678633,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"人生第一次見到一個呀叔流淚","createTime":"2019-10-27T17:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T18:15:47.000Z","uid":319687,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ed091777dc7dbc0b5267956e54a1bbdfca3925b6","tid":1678633,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:53:45.000Z","msg":"今日發夢去佐旺角<br />\n見到個50-60既呀叔坐佐係個樓梯口<br />\n一拿手拿住舊冰&quot;夫&quot;另一隻手碗<br />\n一邊飲泣地哭<br />\n<br />\n我就好心走個去問佢點樣整親<br />\n佢唔肯講<br />\n我再問使唔使叫FA,<br />\n佢又話唔使<br />\n另一些人走去問使唔使幫你叫白車<br />\n佢又話唔使<br />\n不過我都大聲咁叫FA,<br />\n好快佢又唔話唔使之後走佐<br />\n<br />\n後來有另一個途人同我講<br />\n呢位呀叔原來頭先遇到<span style=\"color: orange;\">私鳥</span><br />\n我當堂嚇一跳, 然後得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早知我就補下飛"},{"pid":"dea3759e9091d1a26f026e808f1aea80fb47a9e3","tid":1678633,"uid":82640,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:55:58.000Z","msg":"仆街成個故仔咁撚有喜感嘅"},{"pid":"30d11c91327959ae3b6bba98235923978c3cea57","tid":1678633,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dea3759e9091d1a26f026e808f1aea80fb47a9e3","tid":1678633,"uid":82640,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:55:58.000Z","msg":"仆街成個故仔咁撚有喜感嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1ef0a1d788fad03d8d3cf24153da993055fd5c","tid":1678633,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:57:54.000Z","msg":"寫得麻麻地，我頂多俾５０分。"},{"pid":"edc3ae75a6fb5b895cf960910c85ddcf70b8084b","tid":1678633,"uid":72034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:58:47.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f070822d260748fb383d2dadd2fc0bc4203c039f","tid":1678633,"uid":2